name: OrdiDoges
description: OrdiDoges is a unique NFT project innovating on the Bitcoin ordinals protocol. This project ingeniously merges the popular Shiba Inu imagery with trendy Bitcoin elements, resulting in a collection of digital artworks that are both amusing and captivating. OrdiDoges is more than just a visual delight; it fully embraces the latest inscription technology, giving each piece a distinctive digital identity and value.
